An irc bot that retrieves the player count - and other data of a steamworks-query -compatible server as described in https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Server_queries

Don't want the irc bot? The steamquery.cpp and steamquery.h work as-is without any other files from this project.

![example](http://valssi.fixme.fi/~viderizer/scr/2014-07-11_23-36-01.png)
